    <lb n="16"/>μὴ δε<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">όν</supplied>τως γένηται. ἐρρῶσθαί σε <expan>εὔχο<ex cert="high">μαι</ex></expan>. διὰ Ἀου<hi rend="diaeresis">ι</hi>λᾶ τοῦ κ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">α</supplied>ὶ <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">Δ</supplied>ιονυσίου <expan>βοηθ<ex cert="high">οῦ</ex></expan>. 

